fter the finances while JOhn Soet is away (2014, August-September)','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2014-08-27 04:49:16',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1409114956;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(34,'Needs prayer re depression, sickness','Eric\'s latest bout of sickness has the capacity to really lay him low.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2014-08-27 04:51:44',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1409115104;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(35,'Knee pain','Suffers from constant pain from a knee accident years ago. On opiods for that. Also suffers from mild depression. Off work at the moment, awaiting a disability pension\r\n','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2014-08-27 06:29:09',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1409120949;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(36,'Going away for a few weeks','Myra is off to see her brother and sister over east and to attend a wedding. She is still in a fragile emotional state. Worried about the flight. She is also worried that her brother\'s \"in your face\" approach will be beyond her - that she won\'t be able to cope.','no_action',NULL,0,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2014-09-02 01:17:33',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1409620653;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(37,'Can\'t drive herself','Would normally need a lift','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2014-09-02 01:27:41',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1409621261;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(38,'Feeling down','Val finds herself feeling flat quite often.\r\nShe is happy to help, but not to lead anymore.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2014-09-13 03:28:44',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1410578924;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(39,'Back from Holiday','Saw John - had a great time away for two months. Extended family situation is still difficult. ','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2014-09-13 03:29:30',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1410578970;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(40,'Pastoral Visit','Saw Gloria yesterday. Heard something of her background. COnsiders CBBC one of the friendliest churches she\'s ever been at. Is quite a reader of theoligical books. Spent most of her life at Riverview. Attended Rhema for a conference in south africa. Spent some time in a Lutheran church (after Riverview, prior to CBBC). Prayed holding hands.  \r\n\r\nHas grandchildren in the area. \r\n\r\nHas been in Singleton since January 2014.\r\nTries to make it to church as often as she can - actually retired, but was asked to come back and look after (an old lady?) on Sundays.\r\n\r\nHad a good conversation about faith and doubt. She is one who \"just believes\". Talks about why doubt isn\'t bad. Shared that I myself am one who often doubts - and that we\'re all different. Also shared that despite my doubts, I absolutely hold fast to Jesus being God. \r\n\r\nTalked about trust and faith and how, whether we are aware of it or not, our trust is based on evidence.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2014-09-16 03:47:56',1,'2014-09-16 11:48:32','a:2:{i:1410839276;s:7:\"Created\";i:1410839312;s:1979:\"Updated by Nicholas Van Oudtshoorn (#1)\nDetails changed from \"Saw Gloria yesterday. Heard something of her background. COnsiders CBBC one of the friendliest churches she&#039;s ever been at. Is quite a reader of theoligical books. Spent most of her life at Riverview. Attended Rhema for a conference in south africa. Spent some time in a Lutheran church (after Riverview, prior to CBBC). Prayed holding hands.  \r\n\r\nHas grandchildren in the area. \r\n\r\nHas been in Singleton since January 2014.\r\nTries to make it to church as often as she can - actually retired, but was asked to come back and look after (an old lady?) on Sundays.\r\n\r\nHad a good conversation about faith and doubt. She is one who &quot;just believes&quot;. Talks about why doubt isn&#039;t bad. Shared that I myself am one who often doubts - and that we&#039;re all different. Also shared that despite my doubts, I absolutely hold fast to Jesus being God. \" to \"Saw Gloria yesterday. Heard something of her background. COnsiders CBBC one of the friendliest churches she&#039;s ever been at. Is quite a reader of theoligical books. Spent most of her life at Riverview. At