\nHelen requested prayer that people would see God\'s love through them.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2014-10-14 03:59:22',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1413259162;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(46,'Pastoral Visit','Visited last week. Lyn recovering well from her collapse/faint. Eric feels guilty about putting her under so much pressure. Eric expects his radiation treatment to finish early November.\r\n','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2014-10-14 04:00:21',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1413259221;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(47,'Visitation','Visiting 16 January 2015\r\nJim still not walking properly after a fall.\r\nMargaret sounds tired (but I thought she was a teenager answering the phone! :-) )','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2015-01-14 06:42:49',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1421217769;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(48,'Attending post carols','Erika friends with Francesca Phillips. Peter wants her baptised - spoke, agreed to something more along the lines of dedicaation.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2015-01-21 02:21:05',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1421806865;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(49,'Baptism','Visited and spoke regarding the baptism issue. They were a bit concerned - thought that perhaps we wouldn\'t be a baptist church if we ammended the consitution to allow for people who were baptised as infants to become members.\r\n\r\nJim not well after falling - struggling. Margaret not 100% - just old age, I think.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2015-01-21 02:27:23',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1421807243;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(50,'Dropped off passport applications','Had to sign and fill in their passport applications. There\'s a possibility they might have to leave the country for work. Colin and I are keeping each other accountable to pray daily.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2015-01-21 02:28:15',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1421807295;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(51,'Some suggestions','1. Ministry reports on Sunday mornings - reporting what\'s meant something to you.\r\n\r\n2. Prayer is VITAL. Provide regualr prayer notes, prayer