 just gone. Spoke about how we always do what we want to - but that we want to follow Jesus. Spoke about *why* he wants to be holy.\r\n\r\nBrett\'s car blew up on Australia Day - engine kaput. Would cost about $9000 to fix - a write off.\r\n\r\nMelinda is \"nesting\" in preparation of the baby in about 6 months\' time. She is still not all that keen on the church, but tolerates Brett\'s trusting Jesus.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2016-02-03 07:06:25',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1454483185;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(112,'Pastoral Visit','Went to visit the other day. Going well.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2016-02-10 05:27:22',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1455082042;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(113,'Visit','Went to visit last week, to sign documents for Tarinka\'s citizenship. \r\n\r\nWas a joke about Tarinka wanting to marry her girlfriend/partner - Susanne said only when she was dead. Didn\'t say anything - but need to be clear that that isn\'t something the church will every condone.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2016-02-10 05:28:38',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1455082117;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(114,'Kenly','Kylie Rogan(?) phoned today. Had met a woman at the Op Shop, running away from her abusive husband. Had been fetched from friends where she\'d gone. Was told in the car all that he was going to do to her, jumped out at the petrol station. Was in a previous relationship that also was physically abusive. \r\n\r\nKylie is passing on my number to her, so that I can try and link her in to some support networks. \r\n\r\nKylie is also contacting the police to report what she\'s had.\r\n\r\nKylie has been through an abusive relationship in the past. This was a God thing - she was in the right place at the right moment, and the woman even recognised her from SIngleton PS years ago. Kylie wasn\'t meant to be there at all.\r\n\r\nKylie pointed out this isn\'t just to save her physically, but also for support - and to introduce her to Jesus.','pending',NULL,1,NULL,'2016-05-31',1,'2016-02-10 08:30:41',0,NULL,'a:4:{i:1455093041;s:7:\"Created\";i:1455093055;s:95:\"Updated by Nicholas Van Oudtshoorn (#1)\nAction Date changed from \"17 Feb 2016\" to \"15 Feb 2016\"\";i:1457676163;s:95:\"Updated by Nicholas Van Oudtshoorn (#1)\nAction Date changed from \"15 Feb 2016\" to \"18 Mar 2016\"\";i:1464056731;s:95:\"Updated by Nicholas Van Oudtshoorn (#1)\nAction Date changed from \"18 Mar 2016\" to \"31 May 2016\"\";}'),(115,'Pastoral visit','Visited today - had a good chat, just about life. \r\nSpoke a bit about the church - how we need more young people. No tangible ideas on how to go about doing that.\r\nSpoke about how many in the church are starting to creak.\r\nRhea won\'t be able to attend MOPS, since Tuesday doesn\'t work for her. She spoke to Leonora/Robyn? about making sure Paige\'s mum got the details of MOPS, since Paige didn\'t really seem to be taking it in last week.','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2016-02-11 09:42:17',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1455183737;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(116,'Partner of Tarinka','','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2000-01-01',1,'2016-02-12 02:14:46',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1455243286;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(124,'SMS Sent','Hi David! Missed you guys on Sunday - and just wanted to say hope you\'re keeping well! God bless, Nick','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2016-02-16',1,'2016-02-16 05:49:43',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1455601783;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(125,'SMS Sent','Hi Charmaine! Missed you on Sunday - and just wanted to say hope you\'re keeping well! How is Isaac settling back into work back at the mine again? God bless, Nick','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2016-02-16',1,'2016-02-16 05:50:26',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1455601826;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(126,'SMS Sent','Hi Sharon! Missed you guys on Sunday - and just wanted to say hope you\'re keeping well! God bless, Nick','no_action',NULL,1,NULL,'2016-02-16',1,'2016-02-16 05:50:58',0,NULL,'a:1:{i:1455601858;s:7:\"Created\";}'),(127,'SMS Sent','Hi Matthew! Missed you guys on Sunday - and just wanted to say hope you\'re keeping well! Also, 