INSERT INTO `note_comment` (`id`, `noteid`, `creator`, `created`, `contents`) VALUES (1,53,1,'2016-01-21 03:43:43','Done'),(2,62,1,'2016-01-21 04:40:22','Moved to family note'),(3,63,1,'2016-01-21 04:42:24','Charmaine phoned back. Her phone number has changed. \r\n\r\nWill speak to Isaac about catching up. A bit stressful waiting to hear if he\'s got the job he applied for.\r\n\r\nSeemed a bit hesitant about being visited - might just be her personality.\r\n\r\nIf I don\'t hear back from her by next week, phone again.'),(4,60,1,'2016-01-21 08:14:37','Managed to get through to Myra. She almost had to go to the hospital - but is now okay. Looking forward to a visit in the new few days.'),(5,60,1,'2016-01-27 09:53:03','Had a good visit. Still feeling very low most of the time. Took her out for coffee. Taryn gave her a lift in to church the next day'),(6,61,1,'2016-01-27 09:54:02','Visited today. A good visit. Possible over-sharing by the pastor?\r\n\r\nSpoke about outreach and the church - how this year we need to do more to reach out. Came away with some good ideas.\r\n\r\nJohn really likes the alpha course.'),(7,82,1,'2016-01-27 10:04:30','Sent SMS'),(8,70,1,'2016-01-27 10:04:57','Away on holiday!'),(9,71,1,'2016-01-27 10:05:14','Away on holiday'),(10,73,1,'2016-01-27 10:06:06','Sent SMS'),(11,86,1,'2016-01-27 10:07:17','Sent SMS'),(12,71,1,'2016-01-27 10:10:46','On holiday'),(13,74,1,'2016-01-27 10:11:18','Sent sms'),(14,75,1,'2016-01-27 10:12:20','Didn\'t send sms'),(15,88,1,'2016-01-27 10:12:33','Didn\'t send sms'),(16,77,1,'2016-01-27 10:14:23','Sent sms'),(17,90,1,'2016-01-27 10:14:37','Sent sms'),(18,89,1,'2016-01-27 10:15:08','Sent sms'),(19,72,1,'2016-01-27 10:16:05','Sent sms'),(20,85,1,'2016-01-27 10:16:23','Sent sms'),(21,89,1,'2016-01-27 10:22:37','Reply back: Missed u guys too. Say greetings and wishes for the year to you and your lovely wifeMissed u guys too. Say greetings and wishes for the year to you and your lovely wife\r\n\r\n'),(22,101,1,'2016-02-01 07:41:50','Reply:\r\nHi,l sorry, but we ended up very busy. We were at PMH with Francesca all weekend as she cut her hand open with a Stanley knife on Friday night. Surgery was on Sunday around 2:30. Was supposed to be on Saturday at 9:30.'),(23,102,1,'2016-02-01 07:43:43','Reply:\r\nHi,l sorry, but we ended up very busy. We were at PMH with Francesca all weekend as she cut her hand open with a Stanley knife on Friday night. Surgery was on Sunday around 2:30. Was supposed to be on Saturday at 9:30.'),(24,102,1,'2016-02-01 07:44:02','See reply in David Phillips\' note'),(25,101,1,'2016-02-01 07:44:09','Reply: \r\n\r\nWow - that\'s terrible :-(Praying everything heals quickly. Let us know if there\'s anything we can do.\r\n'),(26,107,1,'2016-02-01 07:45:06','Cut through artery and muscles!'),(27,101,1,'2016-02-01 07:46:48','Reply: Francesca is home with her hand in plaster as she is not allowed to move her thumb. She cut through her artery and muscles. Should take around 8 weeks to heal fully.\r\n\r\nMy reply: Wow :-( Poor girl - that\'s a loong time :-('),(28,101,1,'2016-02-01 07:48:18','Yes. She will miss most of her gum comps.\r\n\r\nreply: :-(\r\n'),(29,102,1,'2016-02-01 07:51:15','    Reply:\r\n\r\n    Wow - that\'s terrible :-(Praying everything heals quickly. Let us know if there\'s anything we can do.\r\n\r\n    Reply: Francesca is home with her hand in plaster as she is not allowed to move her thumb. She cut through her artery and muscles. Should take around 8 weeks to heal fully.\r\n\r\n    My reply: Wow :-( Poor girl - that\'s a loong time :-(\r\n\r\n    Yes. She will miss most of her gym comps.\r\n\r\nMy reply: :-(\r\nReply: But at the end of it she should have full use of her hand again, which is the main thing.\r\n\r\nMy reply: So glad to hear it!'),(30,101,1,'2016-02-01 07:53:25','All this was from Sharon - here\'s what david wrote:\r\nHi :) \r\nhere\'s why we weren\'t there... (picture?)\r\nThat\'s Franceca in emergency after they\'d stitched up the artery she\'d managed to cut\r\n\r\nMy reply: Sharon\'s just been telling me about it... Sounds awful - but glad to hear they reckon it\'ll all work out well in the end...'),(31,100,1,'2016-02-01 10:05:00','Reply:\r\n\r\nThanks Nick\r\nGod bless'),(32,106,1,'2016-02-01 11:10:33','Replied:\r\n\r\nCheer mate im good just work mostly been doing nothing dueing the week and workn weekends god bless how yous been'),(33,107,1,'2016-02-10 05:26:22','Seems to be doing okay. Came to youth last Friday.'),(34,116,1,'2016-02-12 02:15:47','Need to be loving, but also clear that God and as such his church doesn\'t condone their living together.'),(35,128,1,'2016-02-16 05:55:56','Reply: Hi, Nick. We had a day trip for Valentine\'s Day on last Sunday:-) Hope you and Taryn also had a great day. Will see you soon. Cora.'),(36,128,1,'2016-02-16 05:56:26','Reply: Nice :-) see you:-)'),(37,127,1,'2016-02-16 05:57:06','Reply: Hi Nic, thank you! Let\'s read next week? God bless!'),(38,127,1,'2016-02-16 05:57:31','Reply: Sounds good:-) Thank you'),(39,133,1,'2016-02-23 06:10:24','Reply: All well. Mark had last cricket match for season on Sunday .....\r\n'),(40,132,1,'2016-02-23 06:11:28','Reply: All good. I will be at practice yomorrow night. '),(41,140,1,'2016-02-29 04:41:30','Reply: Thanks Nick, and all the best for Taryn on Thursday. Might not be there every Sunday, but we haven\'t forgotten you guys, especially Taryn :)'),(42,139,1,'2016-02-29 04:43:08','Reply: Thanks we r will be home 2morrow night viv:)'),(43,139,1,'2016-02-29 04:43:47','Reply: Enjoy the rest of your time away :-)'),(44,145,1,'2016-02-29 04:46:20','Reply: Yes, 9:30 Wednesday. See you then!\r\nMy Reply: Excellent!'),(45,142,1,'2016-02-29 04:48:49','Reply: Thanks for thinking of me. Everything is fine here. How is Taryn?\r\n\r\nMy reply: Pleasure :-) She\'s doing ok, thank you! Just waiting for the op...'),(46,146,1,'2016-02-29 05:23:17','Reply: Hi Nick. How are you and taryn? We are all good. Just busy with do something with Brook after the whole week work. :-) I just heard about Taryn has a surgery to for on this Thursday morning? Hope she is all good.'),(47,150,1,'2016-03-11 05:56:52','Tried phoning Friday 11 March - left message.'),(48,149,1,'2016-03-11 05:57:21','Didn\'t phone - saw at music group. Doing okay.'),(49,148,1,'2016-03-11 06:02:03','Phoned 11 Martch. Had a difficult week. Jim collapsed, ambulance to hospital.\r\nSeems to be okay now.\r\nCheck how Jim is going in a week'),(50,114,1,'2016-03-11 06:02:43','Tried phoning - no reply.'),(51,150,1,'2016-03-11 06:04:47','Spoke with John. Both busy getting ready for moving house, decluttering etc. Both tired.'),(52,93,1,'2016-03-11 06:13:31','Spoke with Leonora.\r\nTheir long weekend away went well. Daughter\'s husband (Paul?) ended up cancelling his trip and going along with them. Daughter has no self-confidence - thinks \"how can *I* look after kids?\" etc. Going to see a psychologist on Wednesday.\r\n\r\nWillie\'s son got almost? pneumonia, Willie also sick.\r\nWillie can\'t make it to Men\'s breakfast tomorrow because he has to go and help his son with the newspapers, since one of their workers has had to go in to hospital.\r\n\r\nNeed to visit again, talk on the phone was very superficial?'),(53,63,1,'2016-03-11 06:14:10','Need to see about having them over for a meal or something. Isaac goes back to the mines in the next few days.'),(54,157,1,'2016-04-11 05:44:47','Reply: We are both sick and poor Willie is in Malaysia with all those boys and he said it is stinking hot there! He said last night at 3am it was 30 degrees!'),(55,162,1,'2016-05-24 02:23:33','Contact to see if I can pop in Friday morning'),(56,59,1,'2016-05-24 02:24:27','Pam\'s being doing a FANTASTIC job visiting people.\r\n\r\nShe\'s also about to be officially voted in as a member of the church! :-)'),(57,114,1,'2016-05-24 02:25:31','Didn\'t try again. Kylie phoned me a while back to say she\'d had a phone call from the partner of Kenly. Phone call was... strange. Didn\'t want to get involved. Not sure that there\'s much we can do. Keep praying.'),(58,63,1,'2016-05-24 02:26:00','Need to phone again, preferably when Isaac is back.'),(59,183,1,'2016-06-28 07:51:48','Reply: Thanks nick    feeling better\r\nviv\r\n\r\nReplied: Glad to hear it :-)\r\n'),(60,184,1,'2016-07-25 03:34:40','Spoken with Willie.'),(61,114,1,'2016-07-25 03:40:10','Not sure where this ended up...'),(62,195,1,'2017-08-07 10:53:54','Spoke to Willie. Difficult situation.');
